## Privacy Policy

### Effective Date: 02-Dec-2024

Thank you for using the Sudoku Game Bot ("the Application") on Discord. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle information in connection with your use of the Application.

### 1. No Data Collection
We are committed to your privacy and have designed the Application to ensure that:
- No personal information, such as usernames, Discord IDs, or email addresses, is collected, stored, or processed.
- The Application does not record or retain any gameplay data, including scores, playing styles, or user behavior.
- All interactions with the Application occur within the Discord platform and are not logged or stored beyond the duration of the session.

### 2. How the Application Works
The Sudoku Game Bot operates entirely through Discord’s messaging platform. The Application processes commands and generates responses in real-time. Once the session ends, all interaction data is discarded and not stored.

### 3. Third-Party Services
The Application does not use any third-party services or integrations to process or store data. All processing occurs within the confines of Discord’s servers and infrastructure.

### 4. User Responsibilities
While using the Application, users should:
- Refrain from sharing any sensitive or personal information within their interactions with the bot.
- Follow Discord’s Community Guidelines to ensure a safe and enjoyable experience for all users.

### 5. Security
The Application is designed to prioritize user security by:
- Ensuring no data is retained beyond the session.
- Operating solely within Discord’s secure environment.
- Not requiring any additional permissions or access beyond the basic functionalities needed for gameplay.

### 6. Children’s Privacy
The Application is intended for general audiences and does not knowingly collect or process data from users of any age, including children under 13 years old.

### 7. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to update or modify this Privacy Policy at any time. Any changes will be posted here with an updated "Effective Date." Continued use of the Application after changes are made constitutes acceptance of the updated policy.

### 8. Contact Information
If you have any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, please contact us at Discord Server

Thank you for trusting the Sudoku Game Bot. We are committed to providing a safe and enjoyable experience for all users.

